  "text": "where Γ is given by (5ii) and α = 2 ln(2)/[3c ms (Re t 1/2 − 1)] with c ms = 0.28. Charlette et al. [CITATION_1] reduced the input parameters to only u Δ /S L and Δ/δ c using the expression (denoted as FSDCH)",
